==Administrative Divisions<ref>[http://www.xzqh.org/html/list/78.html 营口市-行政区划网]</ref>== There are 5 [[Subdistrict (China)|subdistricts]] and 11 [[Town (China)|towns]] under the city's administration.
Subdistricts: *[[Shiqiao Subdistrict, Dashiqiao|Shiqiao Subdistrict]] (石桥街道), [[Qinghua Subdistrict, Dashiqiao|Qinghua Subdistrict]] (青花街道), [[Jinqiao Subdistrict]] (金桥街道), [[Gangdu Subdistrict]] (钢都街道), [[Nanlou Subdistrict]] (南楼街道)
Towns: *[[Shuiyuan, Dashiqiao|Shuiyuan]] (水源镇), [[Gouyan]] (沟沿镇), [[Shifo, Dashiqiao|Shifo]] (石佛镇), [[Gaokan]] (高坎镇), [[Qikou, Liaoning|Qikou]], [[Huzhuang]] (虎庄镇), [[Guantun]] (官屯镇), [[Boluopu]] (博洛铺镇), [[Yong'an, Dashiqiao|Yong'an]] (永安镇), [[Tangchi, Dashiqiao|Tangchi]] (汤池镇), [[Huangtuling]] (黄土岭镇), [[Zhoujia]] (周家镇)
